'desc': [u'

Curlisto Bio-Curl Shampoo - Imported (237 ml)

Curlisto Bio Curl Shampoo 8 oz. Curlisto Bio Curl Shampoo 8 oz A moisturizing shampoo for damaged or chemically treated hair. Contains natural oils and fatty acids to cleanse and protect against dryness and brittleness. Great for dry and frizzy curl types. This shampoo was specifically designed for people who use chemicals on their hair but has been proven to be very beneficial to clients who have tight coily curls. Key ingredients promote healthy hair by moisturizing and protecting the hair shaft. Directions: Apply to wet hair and work into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if necessary. Follow with Bio-Curl Conditioner. Ingredients: Water Sodium Laureth Sulfate Disodium Cocoamphodiacetate Cocamide DEA Yeast Extract Glycine Soja (Soy-Bean) Oil Sesamum Indicum (Sesame) Seed Oil Zea Mays (Corn) Oil disodium EDTA glycol stearate benzophenone-4 citric acid methylparaben propylparaben diazolidinyl urea phenoxyethanol fragrance yellow 5.
